<taxonomicName id="D3D84DA4D062C6719FE4F90F8EC5897F" authorityName="Santschi" authorityYear="1911" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Plagiolepis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plagiolepis pygmaea subsp. var. var. barbara" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="183" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="variety" species="pygmaea" subSpecies="var." variety="barbara">Plagiolepis pygmaea var. barbara</taxonomicName>
Santschi, 1911 Two type workers were investigated from NHM Basel, labelled &quot;Kairouan Tunisie Santschi. 1903&quot;, &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="58BA8FCDBEEAFF00A24A2CFB2099F033" authorityName="Santschi" authorityYear="1911" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Plagiolepis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plagiolepis barbara" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="183" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barbara">Plagiolepis barbara</taxonomicName>
type Sant&quot;, &quot;v. 
<taxonomicName id="904271A63A7606D924D54A380A903B74" authorityName="Santschi" authorityYear="1911" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Plagiolepis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plagiolepis barbara" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="183" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barbara">Plagiolepis barbara</taxonomicName>
type Sant&quot;, &quot;ANTWEB CASENT0912428 top specimen&quot;.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6046A59B1F118394ECA60B2F49DE5CA7" pageId="0" pageNumber="183">
<taxonomicName id="81B46037AD13C7A1BE9B2D30BBE12C8C" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Plagiolepis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plagiolepis maura" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="183" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maura">Plagiolepis maura</taxonomicName>
Santschi, 1920 [syn. 
<taxonomicName id="5E2B1DBFE344F7CAAA96B3851D73C488" authorityName="Santschi" authorityYear="1911" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Plagiolepis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plagiolepis barbara" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="183" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barbara">Plagiolepis barbara</taxonomicName>
] The collection data published by Santschi are &quot;Maroc: Mogador (Vaucher), avril 1905, types w, m,g. Tanger (Vaucher), Rabat (Thery)&quot;. One type worker was morphometrically investigated from NHM Basel, labelled &quot;4.905 Mogador Vaucher&quot;, &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="A5F8CC1DAA1113EE25CF5B8BD8D101DF" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Plagiolepis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plagiolepis maura" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="183" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maura">Plagiolepis maura</taxonomicName>
type Sants&quot;, &quot;ANTWEB CASENT0912424&quot;. This specimen belongs to the true type series as Santschi published only the Mogador specimens as types. Furthermore, no specimens in the Santschi collection from Tanger and Rabat are labelled as 
<taxonomicName id="289C9520E62C654F9B0624F988E8E082" family="Formicidae" genus="Pl." higherTaxonomySource="treatment-meta" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pl. maura" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="183" rank="species" species="maura">Pl. maura</taxonomicName>
or as types.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
